### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### 1. Upload Receipt
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="travelRequestId"

1
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

HOTEL
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="issueDate"

2024-11-01
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Hotelrechnung für Geschäftsreise nach Berlin
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="amount"

150.00
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="currency"

EUR
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="vendor"

Hotel Berlin Mitte
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample-receipt.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< /home/uncleruckus/Documents/uni/2025WS/projekt/VibeSoftwareEngineering/TravelReimburse/backend/api-requests/ReceiptsJetbrains/sample-receipt.pdf
