### 2. Get Receipt by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1


### 3. Get Receipts by Travel Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/receipts/travel-request/1


### 4. Update Receipt
PUT {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Hotelrechnung - aktualisiert",
  "amount": 175.50,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "vendor": "Hotel Berlin Mitte GmbH"
}

### 5. Validate Receipt
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1/validate


### 6. Reject Receipt
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Beleg ist unleserlich, bitte erneut hochladen"
}

### 7. Download Receipt
GET {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1/download


### 8. Delete Receipt
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/receipts/1
